    <item>
      <title>静夜思</title>
      <link>https://afrusrsc.github.io/yangyang/posts/tangshi/jingyesi/</link>
      <pubDate>Sun, 12 May 2024 15:53:56 +0800</pubDate>
      <guid>https://afrusrsc.github.io/yangyang/posts/tangshi/jingyesi/</guid>
      <description>唐 李白 明代版 床前明月光
疑是地上霜
举头望明月
低头思故乡
宋代版 床前看月光
疑是地上霜
举头望山月
低头思故乡</description>
